00:03:15.462 --> 00:03:18.260
and understand

00:03:18.263 --> 00:03:21.220
that we must to coexist in the same planet

00:03:24.221 --> 00:03:26.395
begin changing yourself

00:03:26.396 --> 00:03:27.760
